Options -Indexes

# ── CORS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DEVELOPMENT: gunakan "*" agar mudah dites dari localhost.
# PRODUCTION: ganti dengan domain frontend Vercel yang fix, mis:
#   Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "https://boarding.rotibakarngeunah.my.id"
Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "*"
Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Methods "GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS"
Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Headers "Content-Type, Authorization"
Header always set Access-Control-Allow-Credentials "true"

# ── Preflight: balas OPTIONS dengan 200 tanpa eksekusi PHP ──
RewriteEngine On
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_METHOD} OPTIONS
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ $1 [R=200,L]

# ── Clean URL: /api/onboarding -> /api/onboarding/index.php ──
# Jika path tidak menunjuk file/folder nyata, biarkan PHP front-controller
# (di sini tiap endpoint adalah file fisik, jadi cukup mapping folder -> index.php)
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME}/index.php -f
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ $1/index.php [L]
